piah), sehingga biaya makanan yang diperlukan untuk merawat harimau-harimau tersebut sebesar = 550.000 x 10 (untuk 30 hari) = Rp. 5.500.000,- (Lima Juta Lima Ratus Ribu Rupiah) untuk tiap 1 ekor harimau tiap 1 bulannya. Biaya Perawatan / Operasional Diperlukan sekurangnya Rp. 1.000.000,- (Satu Juta Rupiah) per 1 ekor harimau per bulannya, meliputi Obat-obatan dan sebagainya. Biaya Penjaga / Pekerja Penjaga / Pekerja yang secara khusus merawat ke-7 harimau tersebut sejumlah 2 orang yang masing-masing akan mendapatkan hak berupa gaji per bulan serta uang makan siang harian. Gaji Penjaga = 2.400.000 x 2 (orang) = Rp. 4.800.000,- (Empat Juta Delapan Ratus Ribu Rupiah). Uang makan siang = 20.000 x 2 (orang) x 30 (hari) = Rp. 1.200.000,- (Satu Juta Dua Ratus Ribu Rupiah). Total Biaya Sehingga total biaya yang diperlukan tiap harimau per bulan = 5.500.000 + 1.000.000 + 685.700 (Gaji penjaga dibagi 7 harimau) + 171.500 (Uang makan siang dibagi 7 harimau) = Rp. 7.357.200,- (Tujuh Juta Tiga Ratus Lima Puluh Tujuh Ribu Dua Ratus Rupiah). Atau Rp. 51.500.000,- (Lima Puluh Satu Juta Lima Ratus Ribu Rupiah) biaya perawatan untuk 7 ekor harimau. Atau Rp. 154.500.000,- (Seratus Lima Puluh Empat Juta Lima Ratus Ribu Rupiah) untuk biaya selama 3 bulan.</p>', '<p>Dengan penjelasan di atas, Yayasan Artha Graha Peduli bersama GotongRoyongFund berkampanye mengajak khalayak luas untuk ikut berpartisipasi dalam penggalangan dana pencegahan punahnya Harimau Sumatra agar tidak sampai terjadi seperti pada punahnya spesies harimau jawa dan harimau bali, mengingat bahwa apa yang kami lakukan tidak akan sukses tanpa dukungan masyarakat luas lokal dan internasional, tiap individu maupun institusi, pemerhati lingkungan flora fauna, serta pemerintah sebagai pembuat kebijakan.</p>', '<p>2015         : Gotongroyongfund\r\n</p>', '<p>Berikan dukungan anda dengan berdonasi sesuai keinginan anda, kami akan sediakan merchandise/rewards atas sumbangsih anda ikut menjaga kelestarian Harimau sumatra. Semakin besar dukungan anda semakin besar pula apa yang dapat kami lakukan ke depan demi memelihara keseimbangan ekologi fauna, khususnya spesies unik khas Indonesia, Harimau Sumatra</p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Save-The-Sumatran-Tiger-Raise-Awareness/177392625649550', '177392625649550', 'https://twitter.com/GRfund', '611107252494143488', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '12-1-tg-150x150.gif', '12-2-Mekar-3-150x150.jpg', '12-3-IMG_7824-150x150.jpg', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/PLGk_FExozI', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(13, 'Red Dress Runs for B.A.C.A.', '', 1, 1, '2015-04-30', 'We are a part of a world wide social running group that organizes runs around the world to raise mon', '', 'We are a part of a world wide social running group that organizes runs around the world to raise money for local charities.  Each year the local kennel of the Hash House Harriers in Tucson is raises money for a local charity.  This year we are raising money for the local chapter of B.A.C.A. (Bikers Against Child Abuse)  and we need funds to put on the event so registration money from our participants goes directly to the charity.  It is part sporting event, part social event and part party.  Run or walk the course to stops with entertainment and refreshments often supplied by local businesses or purchased with registration money.  Our goal is to have enough funds to operate so all the funds of registration go to B.A.C.A.  The event date is 7/11/2015', '', '2015-05-19', 'protest-300x225.jpg', '500000000', '250000000', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 1, '2015-06-15 02:56:23', '10', 1, '', 'Red-Dress-Runs-for-BACA', 'web_team', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(14, 'Voluntour in Guatemala', '', 1, 1, '2015-04-30', 'Volunteer in Guatemala with International Volunteer HQ! IVHQ has a wide range of volunteer abroad', '', 'Hello! My name is Sharon Wong and on June 11-17, 2015 I will be embarking on my very first voluntourism trip to San Martin Jilotepeque, Chimaltenango, Guatemala, where I and several other volunteers will be working side by side with Guatemalan village children in building a bottle school for them to attend.\r\n\r\nIn Guatemala, children walk miles to the nearest school and do not continue their schooling past elementary because there are no other higher level schools within reach. In addition, the schools that they do have are of poor quality and damaged from their extreme weather conditions, resulting in rain water dripping into the classrooms during rain storms. \r\n\r\nWe will be using &quot;eco-bricks&quot; which are plastic bottles filled with inorganic trash (instead of cinder blocks or bricks), sandwiched in between chicken wire, and covered with cement to form the walls of the school.', '', '2015-05-20', 'P9263467-300x225.jpg', '50000000', '0', 0, '2015-04-30 06:24:40', 1, 1, '2015-06-19 09:04:39', '10', 1, '', 'Voluntour-in-Guatemala', 'me', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(17, 'Winterflame : The Other Side- An Epic Puzzle-Adventure Game', '', 1, 1, '2015-05-26', 'What if the act of saving a loved one leads to the uncovering of a distorted truth? Would you be wil', '', '&lt;p&gt;Have you ever wished that the wind would dance to your fingertips? That you could bend the elements to your will? Lev wishes for these very things as the only Human being raised amongst the magical &lt;em&gt;Frameless&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lev&amp;rsquo;s only anchor in his lonely, magic-free existence is Raina, who has now mysteriously vanished. The pain of having an important part of his life ripped out and the chafing inaction of the other &lt;em&gt;Frameless&lt;/em&gt; awaiting answers from their silent gods, spurs Lev into action. Will Raina&amp;rsquo;s mysterious fate ever be revealed?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', '2015-05-27', 'photo-original.jpg', '650000000', '0', 0, '2015-05-26 03:26:36', 1, 1, '2015-06-04 03:44:07', '12', 1, '', 'Winterflame--The-Other-Side--An-Epic-Puzzle-Adventure-Game', 'Artoncode', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(20, 'Montclair Bread Co.', '', 1, 1, '2015-05-26', 'A bread bakery, with a doughnut addiction, creates a community space.', '', '&lt;p&gt;In May 2012, when I greeted our first customer, if someone told me people would be lining up at our door for doughnuts on Sunday mornings, I would never have believed them. &amp;nbsp;My whole world was centered around baking wholesome artisan breads...hence the Montclair BREAD Company. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;My friend Peter was cleaning out his apartment and he brought me a beautiful copper pot. &amp;nbsp;I showed it to Kyra, a fellow CIA grad who specialized in savory fare. &amp;nbsp;She told me it would hold heat well and would be great for frying. &amp;nbsp;She immediately started begging me to make her doughnuts while we worked side by side on Sunday mornings at the bakery. &amp;nbsp;I caved. &amp;nbsp;The first batch of brioche doughnuts, made in January 2013, yielded 3 dozen rings. &amp;nbsp;We coated them with cinnamon &amp;amp; sugar, ate half of them and put the rest out for sale. &amp;nbsp;They were gone in a hot second. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our second Sunday of doughnuts produced the same results. &amp;nbsp;On Valentine&amp;#39;s Day we made six dozen doughnuts and we introduced Boston Cream for the first time. &amp;nbsp;That poor little copper pot was working hard!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;MBCo''s First Boston Creams - February 2013&quot; class=&quot;fit&quot; src=&quot;https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/003/692/084/2101f6b6ad975cc89004a3979e942045_original.jpg?v=1430232877&amp;amp;w=700&amp;amp;h=&amp;amp;fit=max&amp;amp;auto=format&amp;amp;q=92&amp;amp;s=224cf68d814ef0a279e2eb01fe4c70e0&quot; style=&quot;height:387px; width:516px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;I&amp;#39;m not sure when it happened. Sometime between that first Boston Cream and the line down the street on Mother&amp;#39;s Day, Montclair discovered us. Sunday Doughnuts were a thing!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Label Street -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where the Magic Happens!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;template asset&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;16 Label St rendering&quot; class=&quot;fit&quot; src=&quot;https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/003/686/042/9e8a8dc0bebc165f88fd38869ba3b922_original.jpg?v=1430152557&amp;amp;w=700&amp;amp;h=&amp;amp;fit=max&amp;amp;auto=format&amp;amp;q=92&amp;amp;s=bfac7ab8eb38af124c0ccbfcfbfba466&quot; style=&quot;height:242px; width:605px&quot; /&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;16 Label St rendering&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our kitchen currently occupies about 300 sq ft of our total 600 sq ft on Walnut Street. &amp;nbsp;The baking operation will be moving to a 1,290 sq ft space on Label Street in August, 2015. &amp;nbsp;This is where we will create all the yummy doughnuts, breads, croissants and muffins for Montclair Bread Co.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Time to Make the Doughnuts by Nat Chitwood&quot; class=&quot;fit&quot; src=&quot;https://ksr-ugc.imgix.net/assets/003/694/392/b6329e6053a2891cb70889164f1d6380_original.jpg?v=1430255326&amp;amp;w=700&amp;amp;h=&amp;amp;fit=max&amp;amp;auto=format&amp;amp;q=92&amp;amp;s=17557f90174f511a2bac27d806beb32f&quot; style=&quot;height:398px; width:597px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', '2015-05-31', '3.jpg', '140000000', '0', 0, '2015-05-26 03:47:12', 1, 1, '2015-06-04 03:44:14', '6', 1, '', 'Montclair-Bread-Co', 'Rachel Crampsey', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(22, 'Rumah Aman Anak', '', 8, 10, '2015-06-26', 'Wadah sementara bagi anak-anak korban kekerasan yang membutuhkan perlindungan khusus lainnya', '', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;color:#000; font-weight:bold; font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Anak selaku koban, dimana predator-nya berada di lingkungan paling dekat (keluarga), tidak dapat dikembalikan seketika kepada keluarga dan harus mendapatkan perlindungan khusus.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Who we are:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Komisi Nasional Perlindungan Anak (disingkat Komnas PA) adalah organisasi di Indonesia dengan tujuan memantau, memajukan, dan melindungi hak anak, serta mencegah berbagai kemungkinan pelanggaran hak anak yang dilakukan oleh Negara, perorangan, atau lembaga. Komnas PA didirikan pada tanggal 26 Oktober 1998 di Jakarta.&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;What We Need:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kebutuhan Dana Program :&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Rumah perlindungan anak (1 rumah per lokasi) Rp 410.000.000,-&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Pengadaan peralatan (taman bermain) dan furniture Rp 90.000.000,-&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;The Impact:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;RUMAH AMAN ANAK (Children&amp;rsquo;s Safety House) didirikan dengan maksud untuk menjamin kesejahteraan anak melalui program penanganan anak-anak yang membutuhkan perlindungan khusus yang akan menggantikan peran keluarga melalui berbagai kegiatan, antara lain:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Alternatif keluarga pengganti&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Terapi psikososial&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Konseling&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Dukungan sosial&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Advokasi&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Kegiatan Edukatif dan Rekreasi&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Perawatan medis (bekerja sama dengan rumah sakit dan pusat kesehatan masyarakat)&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Pemenuhan kebutuhan dasar (sandang, pangan, shelther)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Time Line:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Jumlah kasus kekerasan pada anak yang berhasil dipantau dan dihimpun oleh divisi Pusat Data dan Informasi (PUSDATIN) Komnas Anak di Indonesia selama kurun waktu 2010-2014, adalah sbb:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Tahun 2010 : 2.413 kasus, dimana 992 kasus (41 %) adalah kejahatan seksual&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Tahun 2011 : 2.508 kasus, dimana 1.020 kasus (41 %) adalah kejahatan seksual&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Tahun 2012 : 2.637 kasus, dimana 1.075 kasus (41 %) adalah kejahatan seksual&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Tahun 2013 : 1.620 kasus, dimana 817 kasus (50 %) adalah kejahatan seksual&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;bull; Tahun 2014 : 2.737 kasus, dimana 1.424 kasus (52%) adalah kejahatan seksual&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Acknowledgements / rewards :&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Appreciation Card by KomNas Anak&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Wristband &amp;quot;Stop Child Abuse&amp;quot;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- T-Shirt &amp;quot;Stop Child Abuse&amp;quot;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n- Polo Shirt &amp;quot;Stop Child Abuse&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Additional Link :&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Link to Facebook :&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.facebook.com/pages/Komisi-Nasional-Perlindungan-Anak/129063155327&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; https://www.facebook.com/pages/Komisi-Nasional-Perlindungan-Anak/129063155327&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-10&quot;&gt;Link to Twitter:&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/komnas_anak&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; https://twitter.com/komnas_anak&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Social Streams&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot; id=&quot;fb-root&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;fb-page&quo