ikut berkontribusi seoptimal mungkin melalui platform GotongRoyongFund. Mari kita bersama-sama berkontribusi untuk memperbaiki kerusakan sarana dan prasarana di Komnas Anak demi masa depan anak-anak Indonesia yang bebas kekerasan.  </p>', '<p>Sabtu, 27 Juni 2015, sekitar pukul 20.11 WIB</p>', '<p>- Appreciation Card by KomNas Anak\n- Wristband "Stop Child Abuse"\n- T-Shirt "Stop Child Abuse"\n- Polo Shirt "Stop Child Abuse" </p>', 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Komisi-Nasional-Perlindungan-Anak/129063155327', '129063155327', 'https://twitter.com/komnas_anak', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'IMG-20150629-WA0007.jpg', '27-2-02.jpg', '27-3-IMG-20150629-WA0006.jpg', '', 0, '', '', '', ''),
(38, 'Forgotten By The Fatherland (Vergeten Door Het Vaderland)', '', 22, 10, '2015-07-24', 'After independence a whole generation of dutch Indonesian were not allowed to go to the Netherlands.', '', '&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;color:#000; font-weight:bold; font-size:18px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;After the end of the Japanese occupation in 1945 thousands of Dutch children with their Indonesian mothers had to stay behind. The government in the Netherlands refused to include these families.These people were forced to take the Indonesian citizenship or they remained stateless. Seventy years after the decolonization of the Dutch East Indies thousands of very old people live in absolute poverty in Indonesia. They are not entitled to a pension. They feel forgotten by their own country. The Dutch government should take responsibility for these fellow countrymen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Who we are:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;I&amp;#39;m a Dutch correspondent based for almost a decade in Jakarta. I contribute to many papers, magazines and radio stations in the Netherlands and Belgium. I&amp;#39;m the writer of the book &amp;#39;Forgotten by the Fatherland&amp;#39;. I&amp;#39;m a researcher and an anthropologist too. My passion is to write and make radio documentaries about vulnerable people. I don&amp;#39;t want to show their weak side but their strong abilities. Every person has some thing tough inside. If you give them a hand, they know how to fight and stand up for themselves.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;What We Need:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;We need 200 million rupiah for food, shelter and medical care. 25 % goes for food, 25 % for shelter, 15 % for medical care, the rest we want to use for education projects for the grand children of this abandoned old people. Because they didn&amp;#39;t have money for the schools of their children. The second generation also had less change on the labour market. By providing funds perhaps the third generation can break the circle. The fund is for one year.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;The Impact:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The people forgotten by the fatherland will have with your support a decent old age time. Now they have to go some times to the street to beg for food. One old man is a gipsy. He doesn&amp;#39;t have a home. He is 75 but sleeps at night on a wooden brick. The Dutch government, the multinational companies from the Netherlands and the NGO&amp;#39;s also have to take their responsibility for these fellow countrymen. They also have to contribute. If you help us to collect the money we can give this abandoned people some sense of honour back.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Time Line:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Acknowledgements / rewards :&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;By all helping this people it will make the bound between the Indonesian and Dutch people more stronger. We can show the world we can take responsibility for each other. Th Dutch came and conquer your country. in 1945 the new republic Indonesian was born. There are no feelings of hate any more but feelings we will and can help each other.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Additional Link :&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr /&gt;\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Images :&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://gotongroyong.fund/uploads/project/11-2-jakarta.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;11-2-jakarta.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://gotongroyong.fund/uploads/project/11-2-jakarta.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://gotongroyong.fund/uploads/project/11-1-ea.jpg&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;11-1-ea.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://gotongroyong.fund/uploads/project/11-1-ea.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://gotongroyong.fund/uploads/project/11-3-surabaya.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;11-3-surabaya.jpg&quot; src=&quot;http://gotongroyong.fund/uploads/project/11-3-surabaya.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:100%&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', '', '2016-02-29', 'Untitled-4.jpg', '200000000', '0', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '10', 22, 'Forgotten by the Fatherland', 'Forgotten-By-The-Fatherland-Vergeten-Door-Het-Vaderland', '', '<p>After the end of the Japanese occupation in 1945 thousands of Dutch children with their Indonesian mothers had to stay behind. The government in the Netherlands refused to include these families.These people were forced to take the Indonesian citizenship or they remained stateless. \nSeventy years after the decolonization of the Dutch East Indies thousands of very old people live in absolute poverty in Indonesia. They are not entitled to a pension. They feel forgotten by their own country. The Dutch government should take responsibility for these fellow countrymen.</p>', '<p>I''m a Dutch correspondent based for almost a decade in Jakarta. I contribute to many papers, magazines and radio stations in the Netherlands and Belgium. I''m the writer of the book ''Forgotten by the Fatherland''. I''m a researcher and an anthropologist too. My passion is to write and make radio documentaries about vulnerable people. I don''t want to show their weak side but their strong abilities. Every person has some thing tough inside. If you give them a hand, they know how to fight and stand up for themselves.</p>', '<p>We need 200 million rupiah for food, shelter and medical care. 25 % goes for food, 25 % for shelter, 15 % for medical care, the rest we want to use for education projects for the grand children of this abandoned old people. Because they didn''t have money for the schools of their children. The second generation also had less change on the labour market. By providing funds perhaps the third generation can break the circle. The fund is for one year. </p>', '<p>The people forgotten by the fatherland will have with your support a decent old age time. Now they have to go some times to the street to beg for food. One old man is a gipsy. He doesn''t have a home. He is 75 but sleeps at night on a wooden brick. The Dutch government, the multinational companies from the Netherlands and the NGO''s also have to take their responsibility for these fellow countrymen. They also have to contribute. If you help us to collect the money we can give this abandoned people some sense of honour back.</p>', '', '<p>By all helping this people it will make the bound between the Indonesian and Dutch people more stronger. We can show the world we can take responsibility for each other. Th Dutch came and conquer your country. in 1945 the new republic Indonesian was born. There are no feelings of hate any more but feelings we will and can help each other.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '11-2-jakarta.jpg', '11-1-ea.jpg', '11-3-surabaya.jpg', '', 1, '', '', '', ''),
(45, 'Sekolah Alam Martha Cendikia', '', 24, 2, '2015-08-05', 'Pendirian Sekolah Alam Martha Cendikia sebagai salah satu sekolah yang mampu mendidik kader handal. ', '', '', '', '2017-08-17', 'Sekolah-Alam-Martha-Cendikia-logo sekolah alam.jpg', '400000000', '0', 0, '2015-08-05 21:36:03', 1, 0, '2015-08-05 21:36:03', '0', 24, 'pendidikan sekolah alam,pesantren,balai karya,lingkungan hijau,menjamin peradaban', 'Sekolah-Alam-Martha-Cendikia', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '');
